article.headline: Spartans hold Roberson scoreless in rout of Gators

images.name: Anderson_Alan 032303 inline
images.caption: Alan Anderson and Michigan State had no problems with second-seeded Florida.

article.story: GAINESVILLE, Fla. (AP) -- David Lee scored 20 points, leading No. 8 Florida to an 107-73 exhibition victory over Team Nike on Tuesday night. Lee was 9-of-10 from the floor and shot 15-of-17 in Florida's two exhibition games. Center Bonell Colas added 16 points for the Gators, Matt Walsh had 13, and Christian Drejer had 12 points and 10 assists. Donta Richardson had 25 points for Team Nike. Florida opens the regular season on Nov. 25 at home against Montana State.
